Class GameManagerAdapter

java.lang.Object
com.example.miniproyecto4.model.Game.GameManagerAdapter
All Implemented Interfaces:
IGameManager
Direct Known Subclasses:
GameManager
public abstract class GameManagerAdapter extends Object implements IGameManager
Adapter class providing default implementations for IGameManager interface. This adapter allows subclasses to override only the methods they need, following the Adapter design pattern. Provides sensible defaults for game management functionality to minimize boilerplate code. Useful for creating specialized game managers or testing implementations.
